    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i deserve respect but it doesnt change the fact that it never actually happens. its just a constant cycle of feeling like an outsider. sometimes i think maybe the fight is just pointless. like what is actually the point of trying so hard when the end result is always the same? it just feels like i'm running a race i can't win.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
